snippet.title: Bad Piggies Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
The Bad Piggies are after the eggs again, as they star in their very first game! http://rov.io/downloadpigs

Can you create the ultimate flying machine and steer them safely to their destination? With more than 60 levels and free updates coming up, you have hours and hours of crashing, exploding and flying pigs!

Like Bad Piggies on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/badpiggies
Follow Bad Piggies on Twitter: http://twitter.com/badpiggies
